data.description: Under contract-accepting backup offers. Beautiful 3/2, 2,070 sq ft home with den/office. It sits on .29 acre lot and boasts an open floor plan, abundant natural light and elegant finishes throughout. Kitchen features appliances and an island and opens up into large family room and breakfast area.  The dining area leads to a screened in lanai overlooking the large backyard.  The master suite is a private retreat with a spacious en-suite bathroom.  Outside, the property offers space for gardening and outdoor activities, along with a two-car garage and ample driveway parking.  The location in Palm Coast provides easy access to beaches, golf courses, parks and various amenities, and is within 30 minutes of historic St. Augustine.  This home is perfect for those seeking the quintessential Florida lifestyle, blending coastal living with convenience.
